subject: Your design at CustomPlanet.com.
first_message:
Hi Hollie,
You need to design one single jersey as the sample.  Create the design on
the front and back. Then, use the roster tool. We will follow that. The
design is just a sample of how you want it to look.
IF you want, send over your roster and design and we can create the order
for you and call for payment.
Thanks!
Chris

Hi Brady,

Sure thing. We can definitely print and text (or send a physical sample, if
you have time). But we only do that if an order is placed. The reason is
because screen print takes a couple hours to setup and do a job.

Question - do you want the gold in the boat stacks and wheel?  To do them
screen printed, we would need to "knock out" those colors and show the hat
color through. Or, if you wanted to keep them we could do printed vinyl.

subject: Your design at CustomPlanet.com.
first_message:
We would have to allow time to order the blank products from our vendors,
print time, and then ship them out. When you order it should give you the
option to choose your own delivery date. I think the absolute soonest we
could do is one week from when you order, and that's with $75 rush
shipping, we have other shipping prices for different dates. When did you
need these by? Also we have to keep in mind that Monday is a holiday so
this may also affect shipping and delivery.

subject: Your design at CustomPlanet.com.
first_message:
Hello,
We could embroider that logo on the front of the hat with the design on the
back as well that is not a problem at all!
We do not have patches that we make here though, we could add a box around
the design with some stitching on top to make the design seem like a patch
when it is stitched onto the hat as well?
Thank you!

fishingthejuice@gmail.com> wrote:

> the front. With the back still saying  "Reel Recognize Reel."
